{"tid":422250,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"逃亡25年躲過追訴期！男性侵鄰居10歲女童...爽獲「免訴」","createTime":"2017-10-03T01:43:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T03:14:53.000Z","uid":122,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60196f0484ffda51d6f80d1dc74b8e77ffff1bfe","tid":422250,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:43:26.000Z","msg":"彰化一名鄭姓男子，1991年間涉嫌多次性侵鄰居10歲女童，經檢方提起公訴後，卻在法院審理時突然逃亡。彰化地院於1992年6月發布通緝，不過鄭男逃亡25年來始終下落不明，法官審酌已超過25年追訴權時效，因此諭知免訴。<br />\n<br />\n現年90多歲的鄭姓男子，1991年7月至10月間涉嫌多次性侵10歲女童，觸犯修正前《刑法》姦淫未滿14歲之女子罪，彰化地檢署於1991年11月14日開始偵查，於1992年1月6日提起公訴。不過在地院審理期間，鄭男趁機逃逸無蹤，彰化地院於同年6月4日發布通緝，但至今仍下落不明。<br />\n<br />\n判決指出，按照修正前《刑法》，鄭男所觸犯的案件追訴期為20年，再加計因通緝而停止時效進行達原定追訴時效4分之1，即為5年，因此本案追訴期合計25年。從實施偵查日至發布通緝日期間有6個月又21日，扣除從提起公訴日開始到繫屬於法院的追訴權時效停止進行期間45日，案件追訴期以於2017年4月7日完成，已逾25年追訴權時效，諭知免訴判決。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/85/89/dd/8589dd79e68f1560078cb972600c974a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F85%2F89%2Fdd%2F8589dd79e68f1560078cb972600c974a.gif&h=69f6dbe2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dfa1fd84e8c6adef28f13aec316692021b358b65","tid":422250,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:44:24.000Z","msg":"入黎睇gif"},{"pid":"8492082685cae98025446dd826908492a7ac5daa","tid":422250,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:45:38.000Z","msg":"應該都死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25b51fd4ab7083b90333994615dd5ddef3b5139","tid":422250,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:48:07.000Z","msg":"香港有冇啲咁既野玩？"},{"pid":"ca472ed8edbe35caff84095945f9b0a0fcad7c13","tid":422250,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該都死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現年90多歲的鄭姓男子</span>"},{"pid":"94a5a03b278acbe2a1079dc5f4e6c7544f854d08","tid":422250,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T01:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入黎睇gif</blockquote><br />\n原來有人追黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b4c28b209063b5867eb119d701be54ef9ab888","tid":422250,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該都死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">現年90多歲的鄭姓男子</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁搵唔到嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb73b31436e62cf86711c9a0e1a6b13c1837997","tid":422250,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:14:53.000Z","msg":"白夜行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}